OL,5, A bid to protect millions of pupils in 
OL,6, England from "the disaster" of future  
OL,7, school and college shutdowns is being  
OL,8, heard in the Commons on Wednesday.     
OL,10,FRobert Halfon, chairman of the Commons 
OL,11,FEducation Committee, is presenting a   
OL,12,FBill arguing schools must remain open  
OL,13,Fas they are "essential infrastructure".
OL,15,FMr Halfon wants ministers to consult   
OL,16,Fthe Children's Commissioner, and allow 
OL,17,FMPs a vote on any future closure plans.
OL,19,FThe government maintains Covid-linked  
OL,20,Fclosures have been a last resort.      
